column1: #Text=What would bother you more in bed , somebody who is overly flatulent , or somebody who speaks in a little baby voice ?
#Text=I never really liked that so much .
#Text=God , let 's see ... would least want to share the bed with ?
#Text=I think probably the baby voice would probably bother me the most .
#Text=Sharin do you find it difficult dating ?
#Text=Obviously because you are away so much it really takes a lot of work to keep things intimate with people I am seeing when I 'm away on the road .
#Text=How do you try to circumvent those problems ?
#Text=I try and keep on tour only three weeks at a time .
#Text=Which does n't work all the time ...
#Text=I try to keep it to that and have some free time at home , which is typically , like , four days .
#Text=And then I try to communicate a lot with the phone .
#Text=What traits do you deplore in other people ?
#Text=Yeah , ignorance of people around them and of the world .
#Text=Which traits do you deplore in yourselves ?
#Text=Do you do anything to get over those things ?
#Text=Yeah , I try , but it 's not so easy .
#Text=But I 've read interviews with you where you talk about the wild party scene in Los Angeles ...
#Text=Yeah , in preparation for this I read where you talked about that in an interview ...
#Text=That must have been me back in the day !
#Text=I 'm old now , you know , settled and I do n't go out now anymore .
#Text=I like to have fun , we have a lot of fun .
#Text=I really like myself a lot , actually .
#Text=I 'm in a very good state ; I have my wife and I 'm very happy and positive ...
#Text=Is that the trait that you deplore in him ?
#Text=Is there a trait that you deplore in Sharin ?
#Text=Well , she 's late , and I hate that .
